## Appeal Points
- Optimized API performance using eager loading
- Modular controller and serializer structure

## Implemented Features
- Posting, deleting, and liking murmurs
- Following/unfollowing users
- Timeline pagination
- User profile views

## Unimplemented Features
- Real-time updates via ActionCable
- Password recovery system

## Impressions
- The project helped improve my confidence with REST APIs, pagination, and component reuse.
